snippet.textDisplay:
I said I wasn’t satisfied after the Vandy & ND wins but fans said I should just be happy they won & get over it... I said the offense was horrible & that Fromm simply isn’t getting the job done... They said I’m not the coach & that Fromm led us to a national title... I said our defense is legit but we’re playing against backup QBs & hasn’t truly been tested, we beat Florida & Aub & I was told I’m not a real fan, idk football & that I should pack my things & go cheer for Ohio st... I said our defense isn’t gonna last against LSU if the offense can’t score TDS instead of field goals, plus if Swift couldn’t run the ball we were done but they said “LSU defense is trash, they have to this many yards to that team, they only scored this much against this team, they gave up over 400yds on the ground to that team”

& what the hell happened yesterday!!!? Fromm missing WIDE OPEN receivers, wrs dropping passes, LSU defense straight SHUT DOWN OUR RUN GAME(but we’re supposed to be RBU🤷🏾‍♂️) LSU scored on their 1st & 3rd possessions of the game, would’ve been more but hey... I’m hearing excuses about Fromm, Swift & Cager being injured... Pickens missing the 1st half and blah, blah, blah but NOT ONCE did I see any of my dawg fans mention how almost every team we’ve faced, they not only just had injuries but KEY INJURIES!!! Remember 2yrs ago against Auburn where Keryyon left the game cause of an injury he sustained the game before??? Don’t recall any dawg fans talking about that but what do I know, I’m not the coach🤣🤷🏾‍♂️
